      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "josStorer/RWKV-Runner",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "A RWKV management and startup tool, full automation, only 8MB. And provides an interface compatible with the OpenAI API. RWKV is a large language model that is fully open source and available for commercial use."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "josStorer/RWKV-Runner",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "<p align=\"center\">"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "BlinkDL/RWKV-LM",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "RWKV (pronounced RwaKuv) is an RNN with great LLM performance, which can also be directly trained like a GPT transformer (parallelizable). We are at RWKV-7 \"Goose\". So it's combining the best of RNN and transformer - great performance, linear time, constant space (no kv-cache), fast training, infinite ctx_len, and free sentence embedding."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "BlinkDL/RWKV-LM",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "RWKV website: https://rwkv.com (with 150+ papers training various RWKV models)"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "BlinkDL/ChatRWKV",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "ChatRWKV is like ChatGPT but powered by RWKV (100% RNN) language model, and open source."
